Does anyone have season 4 od Babylon 5 ?? I could only find 1-3 here =((

FYI: Crusade is a follow up series that takes place after season 5 of babylon 5. A few of the characters from b5 shows up from time to time but the main cast is new.

It's a good series, well worth watching but not quite as good as the original b5.
13 episodes on one DVD must be a collection of xvid or divx or something?
Ah yes, I checked the file list, they're avi's.  I guess this is not a dvd then.  should be in another category.

Går seint dette her. Men seeder det eg kan. Har desverre ikkje allverden linje. Så ha tolmod.
P.S sorry for the wrong category. It is 13. episodes with a collection of xvid.
